{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","title":"removeAnnotation:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1820","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotation:":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"title":"removeAnnotation:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation"}}}